## Summary
This documentation covers the Amplitude Unified SDK for Swift (beta), which provides a wrapper interface for integrating Analytics SDK (AmplitudeSwift), Experiment SDK, and Session Replay SDK together with unified identity management and synchronized user properties across all three products.

